img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係下話"},{"pid":"9af2e267eefe2994fac4ff87566ffb076d7128a7","tid":1595132,"uid":188690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c93bb0028d1fe27b7c4700a4a74099205cbaf4","tid":1595132,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"網上流傅<br />\niPhone Xs 和 XR 都設有慳電模式，即使手機電池耗盡，仍可以使用設定為特快交通卡的虛擬八達通最多 5 小時。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT209495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT209495&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=87e0db25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT209495</a><br />\n在慳電模式下使用「特快交通卡」<br />\n在 iPhone XS、iPhone XS Max 及 iPhone XR 上，你可以在慳電模式下使用「特快交通卡」。慳電模式讓你快速支付車資，並可在 iPhone 需要充電前提供最長五小時的使用時間。<br />\n<br />\n如要在 iPhone 需要充電時查看可否使用「特快交通卡」，請按側邊按鈕。不過，經常重覆此操作可能會大幅減少預留給「特快交通卡」的電力。如果你選擇關閉 iPhone，就無法使用這項功能。"},{"pid":"be4d9d19a5c70ede9533b3dca9680b004b7f633f","tid":1595132,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9136f97ae6161111e6d1f6251c7dbbb634760123","tid":1595132,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4c93bb0028d1fe27b7c4700a4a74099205cbaf4","tid":1595132,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"網上流傅<br />\niPhone Xs 和 XR 都設有慳電模式，即使手機電池耗盡，仍可以使用設定為特快交通卡的虛擬八達通最多 5 小時。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係下話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9dw3eT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9dw3eT.png&h=28862234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔太清楚 不過 八達通 快啲推出喇屌 等咗好耐"},{"pid":"b72e265205